可能存在 13 亿美元的缺口&lt;/a&gt;。 Zircon Bridging 和 Amber Bridging 本周迫使 MFS 在英国破产，它们指责这家总部位于伦敦的公司使用相同的资产作为多笔贷款的抵押品。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; MFS 的崩溃吸引了巴克莱银行、阿波罗全球管理公司旗下的 Atlas SP Partners 部门、杰富瑞金融集团和 TPG 等公司的支持，这是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/O33uJBS8vxwovTUXqJE6wDI234kCed61zsFJpl6l1hVlRM7Z5At-eXJKYG39B4B5r_jb_qMo3V4gBoNMS7tMDXAXUkZFNGCl6cGJHC6sJPsYNoAIZqSP8U5JDjE1oObQh0fxT3guwYrUWWa-4Y_JgtVgXozj-JxfUSdANgAGGV19GpOiO-vXrbleaTvlWHuLb5DpMQ739NDeMw3HaKoH0gHptjbwXx6LWgYPb7MeM2FYocVU0u83vMm1DQGNuJD32lua0_yrfOpaHC3eqtcqHr3ReFwpjtqxN5C8hrgf4V1Vprmv2CwZWfoBNVagOO0mnzwopNumbcn-izA844x6ZEa7mu163zjaR3tFzK75APFt5qGBOgLikbhZXTo/qPx_9SVmeRuRFyPnwJiong0btDLfyH5D/18" target="_blank"&gt;对银行和直接贷款机构造成影响的最新危机&lt;/a&gt;，并让资产融资成为人们关注的焦点。去年美国汽车零部件供应商First Brands Group和次级汽车贷款公司Tricolor Holdings &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/M1TeqJUAOR_I66sgfwQgWiCynnhOx0S2S78bUqLfYEkyM5jVtvosGnI5hqvwVgr9AcwtMhVNa2s-NpMR7zLZzhopgbliVnTNhz6qB4TjKsuFBXhH5mOBPu0RoP1IjzmWlghFDQgXSc5qddgDqi0le9PFkb6a_OnL8yMtng0JOec8fBeiz5NqnLo6aQRZK9rVBOHz7o13WmXRdoRYM_jKJoft33-aio6bZ7f153uKq073rD1wV1covoyEnqkmLOzfordJPPJoMzRYXRr8fmVNFNa04bv1gsqFUxnbpA-Kl3PJ8PhVFwtwQr6Na6dCbCJlGil9mzhueST2syebv8MdkIEdKwuouLPyiaK3GJ9be3_Ydy95GHjn_mFGCn8/ADAfqBVv8NSUIX2Nsrvb9F1feBUPrqAl/18" target="_blank"&gt;倒闭&lt;/a&gt;时也出现了双重质押的指控。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;弗拉基米尔·普京(Vladimir Putin)全面入侵乌克兰四年后&lt;/strong&gt;，也是俄罗斯对其邻国发动战争的十二年之后，越来越多的证据表明，除了超过&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/FS9EWLPuJtcNFjp8jXmdlYqODHtVaAY8pMN2JGkrsJUFV30TPVt9Ift4PpAVSpND9X8jc50ZeuSAI_jdJFoY4zbWPMsPXCSPh2JvOvEuc4YZXlCM-4vaQwkkxChwSY5Rx9_dmmJcFNaJOsFkY-jWkWI9aaXk3kYwyAllOZcb8H_Ti2uLxcuUlZtxTqqX4-wc7u38se5AX8xt5vdxVeOzUuqtNT9QHOa5mHsSp16pTBl670-wCgSwvML03XeJWsUIe19zB5gYJklkn5QcOFEJkYBSnZxguaqK5HnyQU3E_lN3aIXshr7BoRiW2LURINsRGv5f2NjUiwXmwUWeBmANHe2X4fdvJauetzPqSrUqvSXpcddiUVoC3rv1_pQ/Y_BOoJ2hn5e4qVM1WmJZj_lhQNQQnE_l/18" target="_blank"&gt;120万&lt;/a&gt;士兵、雇佣兵、罪犯和应征入伍者之外，俄罗斯正在付出代价。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;尽管克里姆林宫领导人可能将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/HjabqWqneEL-WRcl3yasoOhnv8VVorYyjqhku3hq9hr2FjXg-q6A0AclflZ2zRwTFHvTwOipEA7LEG4BXxKAKPPnbotkCYU4jcHjXt0YY4x5uF4cZxtue0qp9hGrgf7YRx0bZeo6MgMxMUpm-8_6O5u5LK3z7Sy71MbnAfDQUBhF4ZXMb_pZC7Fpe_4ia-aXtYXdKVSv3sqqnkfADcvBmnMLbJKtoBkkNxJ2dylvS5jb_qr0lpkEI5Sv_9Q6Ofwy6sGVW8zFwgMcSka3yYwyWD6cwKMGSzS2x2lXG1a7Mk0CtZOpQFrETuwXXtFZ-nkDkUoT_AHaO97Nc6EPSatACGRMP9-iFtepM23jP8NUb_rmFXKQLehLnEgV8qc/IiGvxNEIcusNL9YAuSKnFh6or6FsrjJX/18" target="_blank"&gt;注意力转向&lt;/a&gt;东欧和北约联盟， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7B_zxU8l_iBU-uv5rStYDyhzb4M0DKLEZnngVIYGCrl2hfbKrNhw_DGMx4kSYRFYWPRaf8ErqqybdhY7NioI31eMwaBXa5WNWRtromS6uvQ0a6TbQOu-gv3TtnwNilD5uZLDlStWAFTdYLlSPbMeFEG2MembEYrKGE0bsVnZoVZ2KlRmicSMyb0yw0znYUrzLwu-8vj5ndr4vtckLpsaohg1YUen_dsHVQgcEI4E8BgdlWikC4LtXOlAwFF__pVj8HQ5EpczwqNOx9dBq4fetPxyiONC--UmMLeVotgbcbzARWdbPdpbTznIeMWDYcM44u1JTLthMPYjS9GAQEBIR3MNcZNqI1VrU9uUc9k6HWizMd9ng8uIdpEFh6I/U8WkZwkDX9NmK2jDhKe838Guaw2JPNWt/18" target="_blank"&gt;但其最大成员的地位日益削弱&lt;/a&gt;，持续的制裁和收入下降正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/B3JaB4eITLjQ3tOFDiBYrL06K1OZ1eBbCOPRP5FooYaxQbq_1K_12F_GQW754C6D55i_nUmChn4qNPWojdiwWyg5sRd-b62NsPDmayqBs1baHBGNNhSgWlvVHUYfXU06uJ9IB4GG5PndZKW76ICuPWoOTjmprrxL4oyucHuwxqWCD5cclFayRWMSeYJzZ-9BV6PUtTip08EUIn_oOg